  "text": "The cloud shapes and motion depend on many simulation parameters and the initial status. The formation of clouds can be simulated using the complex fluid dynamics of the air [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] , but the process is costly and it is very difficult to adjust the parameters so that the clouds reproduce the desired shapes.",
